name: Nijinewstyle_release_v1
description:
Hello guys, it pretty a long time since i release a new model, to day i present you a new model i had made:
Nijinewstyle_release_v1

This model is train by a buch of imagine i had made with Midjourney and Stable Diffusion This is a very cartoon and illustration bias model so don't except make good photograph imagine with this model
This model had VAE baked
Pls down load yalm file include

For good result i will recommend setup at:
Clip skip 2
Sampler:DPM++2M Karras
Steps:20+

CFG scale:4-8
and Hires Fix is strongly recomend, for me i most use 4X ultrasharp
Embeddings on hands-fix are strongly recommended. (bad-hand v5)

Pls support me if you can:
https://patreon.com/Dtrungkien
